msgid "provenance_statement"
msgstr "Every number in this report was computed by a deterministic SQL query over the organization's own service data. No figure was written by a language model. Each figure carries a receipt below: the exact query, the count of rows it drew from, a content hash of that data slice, and a timestamp."

